 (4,5,2,'{"name":"Aura Wellness","short_description":"Feel The Shift","description":"Aglowsciences Marketing Llp\r\nWe provide some of the finest cbd oils in india, crafted from natural, plant-based ingredients to support your overall well-being. Our formulations are thoughtfully designed to help manage everyday concerns like pain relief, improved immunity, better sleep, and enhanced hair and skin health.\r\n\r\nMade with high-quality extracts and carefully tested for purity and consistency, our products aim to deliver effective, gentle support without disrupting your daily routine. We also extend our range to pet care, offering safe and reliable solutions for your furry companions.","keywords":["CBD Oil"],"logo":"\/storage\/brands\/logos\/sVMuiVRzMNToQOROvNAPwxSV0L076pm2LKILs0IZ.png","banner_path":"\/storage\/brands\/banners\/KRO2jiPwGsHfr5CnAXIhS3uw7YgvueoKx6TbZxVa.png","meta_title":"Aura Wellness | Feel The Shift | Cureza","meta_description":"Our formulations are thoughtfully designed to help manage everyday concerns like pain relief, improved immunity, better sleep, and enhanced hair and skin health","meta_keywords":"Ayurveda, Wellness, Supplements, Personal Care, Immunity, Stress & Anxiety, Digestion, Pain & Joint Care, Energy & Vitality, Sleep, General Wellness","faqs":[{"question":"Are all products authentic?","answer":"Absolutely. All products on Cureza are sourced from verified manufacturers and sellers. We ensure 100% authenticity and quality checks before listing."},{"question":"Is free shipping available?","answer":"Yes! We offer free shipping on all orders above \u20b9499. For orders below this amount, a nominal shipping fee of \u20b949 applies."},{"question":"What is your return policy?","answer":"We offer a 7-day easy return policy for most products. If you''re not satisfied with your purchase, you can return it within 7 days for a full refund."}],"categories":["2","3","4","5"],"concerns":["6","7","8","11","10","12","13"],"purity_standards":["100% Organic & Ayurvedic","Toxin & Heavy Metal Free","Cruelty Free & Vegan Friendly"],"genuine_badge_text":"100% Genuine","brand_vision":"Healing from the roots. We bring you pure formulations compiled with ancient Ayurvedic wisdom, modern standards, and absolute transparency."}','approved',NULL,1,'2026-06-14 00:04:34','2026-06-14 00:04:24','2026-06-14 00:04:34');
