 (3,'https://boheco.com/products/bliss-mints-anxiety-relief-and-focus-mints','BLISS Mints',1599,'BLISS Mints are CBD-powered functional mints designed to support focus while easing everyday anxiety. New-age in format yet grounded in science, each mint contains 20 mg of CBD derived from cannabis leaf extract, combined with time-tested Ayurvedic adaptogens like Ashwagandha, Brahmi, Tulsi, along with calming plant extracts like Chamomile and Lavender.
