 (5,'https://boheco.com/products/sleep-for-better-sleep','SLEEP',1399,'SLEEP Tincture is a clinically trialled, cannabis-leaf-based polyherbal formulation designed to address the root causes of poor sleep by improving sleep onset, duration, and depth in alignment with the body’s natural sleep–wake cycle.
