 (7,'https://boheco.com/products/calm-relaxing-herbal-infusion-tea','CALM',649,'CALM is a herbal infusion tea by BOHECO, formulated to support relief from everyday stress and mental fatigue. Designed for regular consumption, it helps regulate stress response and promote emotional steadiness during demanding days or before rest.

