 (8,'https://boheco.com/products/relax-aromatherapy-roll-on-for-relaxation','RELAX',299,'RELAX is an aromatherapy roll-on by BOHECO, formulated to help ease mental and sensory stress through targeted scent application. Designed for daily use, it supports relaxation by influencing the olfactory pathway, which connects directly to brain regions involved in mood and emotional response.

