 (9,'https://boheco.com/products/combat-targeted-relief-for-severe-pain','COMBAT',1999,'COMBAT Tincture is designed for individuals living with severe chronic and neuropathic pain, where long-term illness and intensive treatments can significantly impact comfort, appetite, sleep, and overall quality of life.
