 (10,'https://boheco.com/products/peace-plus-capsules-natural-pain-reliever','PEACE+ Capsules',299,'PEACE+ Capsules are formulated for adults who require doctor-prescribed stronger, natural pain relief. By working with the body’s Endocannabinoid System (ECS), the formulation helps modulate pain signals, reduce inflammation, and support overall physical comfort.
