 (11,'https://boheco.com/products/peace-plus-tincture-natural-pain-reliever-for-moderate-pain','PEACE+ Tincture',1599,'PEACE+ Tincture is a full-spectrum, cannabis-leaf-based formulation designed to provide natural relief from moderate pain by addressing both symptoms and their underlying triggers. It works by interacting with the body’s Endocannabinoid System (ECS), which plays a key role in pain perception, inflammation, and recovery.
