 (12,'https://boheco.com/products/glide-plus-gel-arthritis-and-joint-pain-relief-gel','GLIDE+ Gel',599,'GLIDE+ Gel is a fast-acting, topical Ayurvedic formulation by BOHECO, designed to provide quick relief from joint pain, stiffness, and inflammation associated with arthritis. Powered by a 3X concentration of Cannabis Leaf Extract, GLIDE+ Gel works with the body’s Endocannabinoid System (ECS) to help regulate pain signals and inflammatory responses at the site of application.

