 (13,'https://boheco.com/products/rescue-migraine-relief-balm','RESCUE',349,'RESCUE is a high-potency balm by BOHECO, formulated to provide effective relief from migraines, cluster headaches, stress headaches, and sinus-related pressure. Designed for intense or recurring episodes, it works locally to reduce inflammatory pain, vascular pressure, and muscular tightness at the source.
