 (14,'https://boheco.com/products/hemp-seed-oil-cold-pressed-multipurpose-oil','HEMP SEED OIL',549,'Himalayan Hemp Seed Oil is a cold-pressed, unrefined oil made from Himalayan-grown hemp seeds. Naturally rich in Omega 3 & 6 fatty acids, along with antioxidants (Vitamin-E), it supports overall wellness from within while nourishing the body externally.
