 (15,'https://boheco.com/products/hemp-hearts-shelled-hemp-seeds','HEMP HEARTS',349,'Himalayan Hemp Hearts are premium shelled hemp seeds that deliver concentrated plant-based nutrition in its purest form. Naturally rich in complete protein, essential fatty acids, and fibre, they help support sustained energy, muscle recovery, and long-lasting satiety throughout the day.

