 (16,'https://boheco.com/products/pristine-patented-skin-healing-cream','PRISTINE',649,'India’s first patented and clinically tested cannabis leaf-based skin cream, PRISTINE by BOHECO is designed to help manage chronic inflammatory skin conditions such as eczema, psoriasis, dermatitis, and persistent dry skin. Clinically tested at the National Institute of Ayurveda, Jaipur, it works locally to reduce itching, rashes, and inflammatory flare-ups while supporting skin repair.
