 (17,'https://boheco.com/products/revive-hair-regrowth-serum','REVIVE',899,'REVIVE Advanced Hair Regrowth Serum combines Ayurvedic wisdom with modern hair science to support visible regrowth, scalp health, and stronger hair density. Powered by Capilia Longa™ - clinically proven turmeric stem cells, and Hemp Seed Oil, it helps stimulate dormant hair follicles, improve scalp microcirculation, and support the natural hair growth cycle.

