 (18,'https://boheco.com/products/mental-health-duo-for-anxiety-relief-and-better-sleep','Mental Health Duo',2788,'The Mental Health Duo is a structured AM–PM wellness system designed to regulate the full stress cycle. By working with the body’s Endocannabinoid System (ECS), the formulations help support emotional balance, reduce mental hyperactivity, and promote deeper rest.
The duo includes:


BLISS Tincture: 45 mg/ml of broad-spectrum CBD to soothe anxiety and stress without sedation

SLEEP Tincture: 22.5 mg/ml of full-spectrum cannabis leaf extract in a 2:1 ratio (~7.5 mg CBD/ml) to support deeper, restorative sleep

Derived from broad and full-spectrum cannabis formulations and supported by adaptogenic botanicals, this system works across both day and night. Calmer days naturally lead to better nights, and better sleep strengthens stress resilience. Used consistently, this AM–PM routine supports sustained mental balance, helping you feel centred, composed, and refreshed every day.','["https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/MHD_-FOP_Peach_fennel_10.jpg?v=1774519516","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/MHD_-Theme_image.jpg?v=1774618319","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/MHD_-Benefits.jpg?v=1775743268","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/Sleep-clinical_trial_results_35f99724-bb5a-4819-ada7-17f0a2bf25be.jpg?v=1775826446","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/MHD_-Clinical_trial_results.jpg?v=1775743297","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/MHD_-Ingredients_Bliss.jpg?v=1775743268","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/MHD_-Ingredients_Sleep.jpg?v=1775743268","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/BLISS-lab_report_73fe5ab6-e2e6-4240-84e6-a2a5dcbefe58.jpg?v=1780465935","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/MHD_CBD-Lab_report_Sleep.jpg?v=1775743268","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/MHD_-How_to_use_Bliss.jpg?v=1775743268","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/MHD-Mind_Balance_loop.jpg?v=1775743268","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/GLIDE_GEL-govt_licensed_formulation.jpg?v=1775743268","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/PDP_DESIRE_trust_builders.jpg?v=1775792488"]',NULL,'imported',NULL,1,13,'2026-06-13 15:56:23','2026-06-13 16:16:52'),
 (19,'https://boheco.com/products/all-day-focus-duo-daily-focus-support','All Day Focus Duo',2969,'All Day Focus Duo combines BLISS Tincture and BLISS Mints to support structured anxiety control and sustained focus across the day. Taken in the morning, BLISS works internally to help reduce daily anxiety, calm an overactive mind, and establish steadier mental control. As a prescription formulation with cannabis leaf extract, it supports regulation rather than short-term stimulation.
The duo includes:


