BLISS Mints: 20 mg/mint of broad-spectrum CBD to enhance focus

BLISS Mints complement this baseline by providing on-the-go focus support during midday slowdowns or high-pressure moments. Together, they help reduce overthinking and maintain clarity from morning through demanding situations.','["https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/ADFD-FOP_mint_10_watermelon.jpg?v=1775824261","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/ADFD-blissmints-blissT-moodshot_2.jpg?v=1776845317","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/ADFD-benefits.png?v=1775824308","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/BLISS_Mint-ingredients.jpg?v=1775824308","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/ARD-Ingredients_Bliss_14c57c85-9f43-4634-a478-06b8da4041a6.jpg?v=1775824308","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/BLISS-lab_report_d5b379bb-72c1-4ddc-9ba0-2698632d18e0.jpg?v=1775824308","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/BLISS-mints_lab_report.jpg?v=1775824308","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/ARD-How_to_use_Bliss_b7d98415-9e1f-4da7-9846-28f96b44c605.jpg?v=1775824308","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/BLISS_how_to_use.jpg?v=1775824308","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/ARD_gorv_licensed_form_3854b67d-6d4b-4e1a-9db4-2392e7eb15bd.jpg?v=1775824308","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/PDP-ADFD-comparison.jpg?v=1775824308","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/ARD_trust_builders_f00ddacd-26de-4361-8071-2ae3d4cc08e6.jpg?v=1775824308","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/ADFD-FOP_peach_10_watermelon.jpg?v=1775824191"]',NULL,'imported',NULL,1,13,'2026-06-13 15:56:25','2026-06-13 16:16:52'),
 (20,'https://boheco.com/products/sleep-well-duo-complete-sleep-support','Sleep Well Duo',1528,'Sleep Well Duo combines BOHECO SLEEP Tincture and RELAX Roll-On to support healthier sleep cycles through a structured internal and external routine. SLEEP works internally to regulate sleep onset, reduce mental overactivity, and support deeper, uninterrupted rest. Clinically tested for insomnia, it contains full-spectrum cannabis leaf extract and calming botanicals suited for both persistent sleep disturbances and irregular sleep patterns.
Each 1 ml of SLEEP contains ~22.5 mg of major cannabinoids in a 2:1 ratio (~7.5 mg CBD per ml)
RELAX prepares the body for rest through targeted aromatherapy applied externally before bedtime. Together, they help reset disrupted sleep rhythms and support more consistent, restorative sleep with regular nightly use.','["https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/SWD_-FOP_Amber_rose_fennel_30.jpg?v=1774519666","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/SWD_-Theme_image.jpg?v=1774614430","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/SWD_-Benefits.jpg?v=1774614430","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/SWD_-Ingredients_Relax.jpg?v=1775826446","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/SWD_-Ingredients_Sleep.jpg?v=1775826446","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/Sleep-clinical_trial_results_35f99724-bb5a-4819-ada7-17f0a2bf25be.jpg?v=1775826446","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/SWD_-Clinical_trial_results.jpg?v=1775826446","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/SWD_CBD-Lab_report_Sleep.jpg?v=1775826446","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/SWD_-How_to_use_Sleep.jpg?v=1775826446","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/SWD_-How_to_use_Bliss.jpg?v=1775826446","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/SWD_-FIX_Sleep_Cycle.jpg?v=1775826446","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/SWD_-Trust_builders.jpg?v=1775826446"]',NULL,'imported',NULL,1,13,'2026-06-13 15:56:29','2026-06-13 16:16:52'),
 (21,'https://boheco.com/products/joint-health-duo-complete-joint-care','Joint Pain Duo',1078,'Joint Pain Duo combines GLIDE+ Gel and GLIDE+ Oil to deliver complete joint care through fast pain relief and deeper long-term support. GLIDE+ Gel provides fast joint pain relief, while GLIDE+ Oil is a clinically tested formulation designed to help manage osteoarthritic and inflammatory joint conditions.While the gel acts quickly to ease pain and stiffness, the oil works deeper to reduce inflammation and improve joint lubrication over time. Together, this fast-and-deep approach supports better mobility, reduced stiffness, and sustained joint comfort with consistent use.','["https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/JPD_-FOP_Glideplus_gel_50_oil_100.jpg?v=1774519622","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/JPD_-Theme_image.jpg?v=1774519622","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/JPD_-Benefits.jpg?v=1774614431","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/JPD_-Ingredients_Glideplus_oil.jpg?v=1775828325","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/JPD_-Ingredients_Glideplus_gel.jpg?v=1775828325","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/GLIDE_Oil-Clinical_trial_results_b8668e96-add4-4785-b721-21fd3596874c.jpg?v=1775828325","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/JPD_-Clinical_trial_results.jpg?v=1775828325","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/JPD_-Freedom_to_move.jpg?v=1775828325","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/JPD_-How_to_use_Glideplus_gel.jpg?v=1775828325","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/JPD_-How_to_use_Glideplus_oil.jpg?v=1775828325","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/JPD_-Gov_licensed_formation.jpg?v=1775828325","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/P