 (22,'https://boheco.com/products/anxiety-relief-duo-dual-support-for-daily-anxiety','Anxiety Relief Duo',2113,'The Anxiety Relief Duo combines the fast-acting support of BLISS Tincture with the calming ritual of CALM Tea, offering a balanced approach to managing everyday anxiety and stress. Designed for daytime use, this duo helps ease mental restlessness while supporting sustained calm through the day.BLISS delivers 45 mg/ml of broad-spectrum CBD, working with adaptogens like Tulsi, Brahmi, and Ashwagandha to help regulate the body’s stress response. CALM Tea, infused with Cannabis Leaf, Chamomile, Lavender, and Ashwagandha, complements this support with a soothing herbal blend that promotes relaxation during breaks or transitions. Together, they create a simple daily routine for steadier mood, calmer thoughts, and better stress resilience.','["https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/ARD-calm-20-bliss-mint-10-FOP.jpg?v=1774519561","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/ARD-calm-bliss-mint-moodshot.jpg?v=1774519561","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/PDP-_ARD-benifits.jpg?v=1775829046","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/ARD-Ingredients_Bliss.jpg?v=1775829046","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/ARD-CALM_ingredients.jpg?v=1775829046","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/ARD-BLISS-lab_report.jpg?v=1775829046","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/ARD-How_to_use_Calm.jpg?v=1775829046","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/ARD-How_to_use_Bliss.jpg?v=1775829046","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/PDP-ARD-anxiety-loop.jpg?v=1775829046","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/ARD_gorv_licensed_form.jpg?v=1775829046","https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0629\/5499\/5925\/files\/ARD_trust_