 (23,'https://boheco.com/products/recover-instant-pain-relief-spray','RECOVER',399,'RECOVER Spray is a fast-acting, topical solution designed to provide immediate relief from muscle pain, sprains, pulls, and sudden injuries. Powered by Full-Spectrum Cannabis Leaf Extract, it works at the area of application to help calm pain and inflammation beyond surface-level sensations.
